==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unpin
<hw>Un*pin"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>pin</ets>.]</ety> <def>To loose from pins; to
remove the pins from; to unfasten; <as>as, to <ex>unpin</ex> a frock; to
<ex>unpin</ex> a frame</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unpinion</ent>⟦br⟧
